(surves 4 people)
start by boiling the milk;
add your suger in it and stir for 1 minute;
add the cardimum cloves;
wait for the mixture to come to a boil;
when the milk starts boiling turn the stove off and add the custurd powder;
stir for 10 seconds and let it cool at room temperature;
then stick it in the fridge for 1/2 an hour to cool;
then on the top add your favorite Fruit & Dryfruites;
surve;



            Enjoy your Custurd!!